N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 15ยง 15.4 - Administration and collection

State Regulations

The Commissioner of Motor Vehicles or his/her employees and
agents shall administer and collect the tax described herein, from the date
upon which this agreement becomes effective and thereafter so long as such
agreement remains in effect. Notes
